<h2 id="recruiting">Recruiting</h2>
<p>We will shortly be advertising for two research positions for this project. One researher will be based at Northumbria University and will have a major focus on the design and implementation of sonifications. The other position will be based at Newcastle University  with a focus on technologically-mediated musical or sonic arts practice.</p>

<p>Both positions are fixed term for 36 months and are fully funded by the Leverhulme Trust.</p>

<ul>
  <li>To apply for the research position <a href="https://www.northumbria.ac.uk/work-for-us/job-vacancies/academic-3241-research-fellow-in-sonification-design-and-aesthetics">follow this link</a>. Closing date 13 September, 2020.</li>
  <li>Details on the post at Newcastle and how to apply will appear here shortly.</li>
</ul>

